      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Paragraph",
      "Content": "Ryo gestured on the unconscious Guiran on the muddy ground. For a muscular man like him, one kick from an 18 year-old knocking him out completely was a surprise, and a bit hilarious."
