      "Dialog": "You could say that again. Thankfully this kid distracted him before Ryo found us- wait, where did he go?",
      "Tags": ""
    },
    {
      "Type": "Paragraph",
      "Content": "Minato turned around, seeing Liam gone. Ryo turned around as well."
    },
    {
      "Type": "Dialog",
      "Character": "Ryo",
      "Dialog": "In any case, I think you should man your stall again, Dad. Your patrons are already waiting.",
